 in Leigh’s work. The response serves to redefine cultural production whilst putting contemporary African products at the fore. The products highlight ALÁRA’s distinctive approach, blending traditional African art forms with contemporary expressions.<\/p><p>ALÁRA’s expertise in African creativity and LACMA’s expansive cultural platform unite to foster meaningful exchange and promote vibrant exchanges of ideas and artistic practices, initially in Los Angeles and extending into ALÁRA’s home site of Lagos. The next phase of our partnership will focus on redefining the role of cultural institutions and exploring innovative approaches to cultural production and storytelling.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_ibawkK"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"custom_class":"wandering_body_text","desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","color_scheme":"scheme-fdd3bfd4-6c4f-4e95-8a6d-a18db543683b","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}},"blog_grid_gallery_KpDzKq":{"type":"blog-grid-gallery","name":"Image Grid","settings":{"custom_class":"","section_color_scheme":"scheme-fdd3bfd4-6c4f-4e95-8a6d-a18db543683b","image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2024-11-14_at_12.49.37_1.jpg","image_2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_0141.jpg","image_3":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AW_information_deck_-_21_07_25-90.jpg","image_4":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AW_information_deck_-_21_07_25-69_b753f71f-c2a3-43dc-91c6-72169b3addb7.jpg","image_5":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AW_information_deck_-_21_07_25-76.jpg","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}}},"order":["main","hero_section_trdqyG","featured_collection_f8JKnQ","image_with_text_X6mXfJ","video_K7LYdy","rich_text_fDFmFc","blog_grid_gallery_KpDzKq"]}